3.1. Contributor License Grant
By submitting a Contribution to the Software, You grant the Licensor a worldwide, non-exclusive, transferable, royalty-free license to use, reproduce, prepare derivative works of, publicly display, publicly perform, sublicense, and distribute Your Contributions and such derivative works under the terms of this License.

